From: Eric Biggers <ebiggers@google.com>
Date: Tue, 1 Apr 2025 15:15:56 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] lib/crc: remove unnecessary prompt for CONFIG_CRC16
Git-commit: 2038af8edae281283ee10e220a3df19dcad3b61c
Patch-mainline: v6.15-rc2
References: jsc#PED-15168

All modules that need CONFIG_CRC16 already select it, so there is no
need to bother users about the option.

